Package PetStoreAPI

Class ItemBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • PetStoreAPI.ItemBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sellable, Stockable, Usable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bedding, Enclosure, Food, Toy
    public class ItemBase
extends java.lang.Object
implements Sellable, Stockable, Usable
    This class is extended by Bedding, Enclosure, Food, and Toy and implements Sellable, Stockable, and Usable and is used to create items for the store inventory.
    Since:
    6/29/22
